{{Quote|If we had some bruallki, we could have bruallki and Menkooro&mdash;''"<br />"''&mdash;if we had some Menkooro.|[[Talon Karrde]] and [[Aves]]|<ref name="The Last Command">''[[The Last Command]]''</ref>}}
'''Bruallki''' was a herd animal used for [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]],<ref name="JS" /> which could braised and eaten formally at dinner,<ref name="HttE">''[[Heir to the Empire]]''</ref> or cold as a light snack.<ref name="TLC">''[[The Last Command]]''</ref> [[Menkooro whiskey]] was considered to be the perfect accompaniment to bruallki, leading to the old saying "If you had some bruallki, you could have bruallki and Menkooro&hellip;if you had some Menkooro."<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|306|Menkooro whiskey}}</ref> [[Talon Karrde]] fed bruallki to his pet [[vornskr]], [[Drang]].<ref name="HttE" /> In a formal dining setting, one should never use a three-pronged [[Fork/Legends|fork]] to eat bruallki.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

